::Prowl::

Prowl looks into Iron Raptor's eyes as she leans back and examines 
their bodies, his arms still around her and his eyes never leaving 
her face.

"Yes," he says, lost in her beauty, "You're beautiful.."

The Maximal leans forward, kissing his one true love once again.
